  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK452">
<l>nilattiyalpā ṉīrtirin taṟṟāku māntark </l>
<l>kiṉattiṉiyalpa tāku maṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As water changes (its nature), from the nature of the soil (in which it flows), so will the character of men resemble that of their associates.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
